      "variant": "main",
      "html": "<h4>Activity</h4>\n<p>Choose the slope and intercept from the bank below that corresponds to each equation.<br></p>\n<p>A: \\( m=3 \\), \\( y\\text{-int}=(0,1) \\)<br><span>B: \\( m=\\frac 43 \\), \\( y\\text{-int}=(0,1) \\)<br></span><span>C: \\( m=\\frac 43 \\), \\( y\\text{-int}=(0,-2) \\)<br></span><span>D: \\( m=-4 \\), \\( y\\text{-int}=(0,8) \\)<br></span><span>E: \\( m=3 \\), \\( y\\text{-int}=(0,-2) \\)</span></p>\n<p>1. \\( -4x+3y=3 \\)</p>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Submit\" data-content-id=\"cebabe07-f2ef-4907-a315-69565d20c30b\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>B</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<p>2. \\( 12x-4y=8 \\)</p>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Submit\" data-content-id=\"55bd1144-4dc9-40f5-9c3d-9cc5f884dcbb\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>E</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<p>3. \\( 8x+2y=16 \\)</p>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Submit\" data-content-id=\"02c86e9d-f8bc-4ae1-9603-56ff119c19e3\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>D</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<p>4. \\( -x+\\frac 13 y=\\frac 13 \\)</p>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Submit\" data-content-id=\"fc294f41-b2ca-4a51-be6f-691af04e81d1\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>A</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<p>5. \\( -4x + 3y = -6 \\)</p>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Submit\" data-content-id=\"564634b0-a373-45ba-b9fb-24bc6ef23774\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>C</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta\" data-button-text=\"Are you ready for more?\" data-fire-event=\"eventShowMore1\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-content\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-prompt\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Submit\" data-content-id=\"55855a71-36ff-4a74-97cf-9c05f769a33c\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"eventShowMore1\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <h4>Extending Your Thinking</h4>\n    <p>Below are the equations from above. Each equation is in the form \\( Ax + By = C \\).&nbsp;</p>\n    <p>\\(&nbsp;-4x + 3y = 3&nbsp;\\)<br><span>\\(&nbsp;12x - 4y = 8&nbsp;\\)<br></span><span>\\(&nbsp;8x + 2y = 16&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;\\)<br></span><span>\\(&nbsp;-x + \\frac{1}{3}y = \\frac{1}{3}&nbsp;\\)<br></span><span>\\(&nbsp;-4x + 3y = -6&nbsp;\\)</span></p>\n    <p>1. For each equation, graph the equation and, on the same coordinate plane, graph the line passing through \\(&nbsp;(0,0)&nbsp;\\) and \\(&nbsp;(A,B)&nbsp;\\). What do you notice about each pair of lines? For example, for the first equation pair, graph \\(&nbsp;-4x + 3y = 3&nbsp;\\) and also the line through \\(&nbsp;(0,0)&nbsp;\\) and \\(&nbsp;(-4, 3)&nbsp;\\).</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>They are perpendicular.</p>\n  </div>\n</div><br>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Submit\" data-content-id=\"f0fc8284-e045-4737-8956-ddcccb1b920a\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"eventShowMore1\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <p>2. Find the \\(&nbsp;x&nbsp;\\)-intercept and \\(&nbsp;y&nbsp;\\)-intercept of each equation. Do you notice a pattern? What are the coordinates of the \\(&nbsp;x&nbsp;\\)-intercept and \\(&nbsp;y&nbsp;\\)-intercept in terms of A, B, and C?</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>\\(&nbsp;(\\frac{C}{A}\\ ,\\ 0),\\ (0,\\ \\frac{C}{B})&nbsp;\\)</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"left\">\n</div>"
    }
  ]
